title: FSU Krishna Lunch
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, International, Buffet, Fast food, Take-out
description: The plate includes salad, rice, four entrees, dessert, and tea. Either vegetarian or vegan. Food is display in a buffet case, and you choose the main entree you want. Open to the the public. Parking can sometimes be difficult. Serve in the 1st floor cafeteria of the Center for Global Engagement.
